Package: ILSAmerge
Type: Package
Title: Merge and Download International Large-Scale Assessments (ILSA) Data
Version: 1.4.2
Authors@R: person(given = "Andrés",
                    family = "Christiansen",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "andres.christiansen@iea-hamburg.de")
Maintainer: Andrés Christiansen <andres.christiansen@iea-hamburg.de>
Description: Merges and downloads 'SPSS' data from different International Large-Scale Assessments (ILSA), including: Trends in International Mathematics and Science Study (TIMSS), Progress in International Reading Literacy Study (PIRLS), and other studies from <https://www.iea.nl/>.
